    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Chess… with robots.</h2><br>Assemble your team of braverBOTS, and challenge other players in this strategic combat game. Each BOT has its own identity and style, but only you can turn them into champions. Plan your turn carefully, using Fuel to move and activate abilities.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157940/extras/e64a719610a1c1f01b1a7015478141c0.poster.avif?t=1726254282\" width=588 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157940/extras/e64a719610a1c1f01b1a7015478141c0.webm?t=1726254282\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157940/extras/e64a719610a1c1f01b1a7015478141c0.mp4?t=1726254282\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Strategic turn-based gameplay, with short high-octane matches. The best of both worlds<br></li><li>Growing roster of braverBOTS, each with unique actions and a secondary mode for additional variety<br></li><li>Random pool of maps, with varying objectives and obstacles. Your team will need to be able to find success on all fields in order to win<br></li><li>Free-to-play, with cosmetics available for purchase to support the developers</li></ul>",
